column5: Got out to do some fishing with a bud last sunday and did ok. Went to a spot that is known to produce and it did. In four hours of fishing I had caught about 4 Quality fish. The first was 4.7 on the digital, the second was bang on 5 and I had a few more in the three pound range. Gotta love Simcoe Smallies.
Nice! Yup! They put up a heck of a fight!
Wow...those are some great looking fish!
Nice fish and a lot of fun fishing for them!
nice smallies man...lol ...the background looks like its one of my spots also....lol...good job
